trinket_paladin_retribution_p1 = """
Trinkets for Retribution Paladin DPS<br />For Trinkets, the most optimal setup is to have 1 active on-use trinket and 1 passive proc/trigger trinket. <br />The recommended route is to simply pick up <a href="/cata/item=68712/impatience-of-youth">Impatience of Youth</a> from <a href="/cata/zone=5095/tol-barad">Tol Barad</a> dailies, and then replace your pre-raid passive trinket <a href="/cata/item=56393/heart-of-solace">Heart of Solace</a> with <a href="/cata/item=65072/heart-of-rage">Heart of Rage</a> when possible. <br /><br /><a href="/cata/item=68712/impatience-of-youth">Impatience of Youth</a> is the best active Strength trinket, and there is no comparable active trinket. The rest of the trinkets are passives. <br /><a href="/cata/item=65072/heart-of-rage">Heart of Rage</a> is the best passive option to pair with <a href="/cata/item=68712/impatience-of-youth">Impatience of Youth</a>, as this is the highest Strength proc we can get, lasts 20 seconds, and has a ton of Expertise that you may need to gear / reforge around. It is also best in slot next phase in <a href="/cata/zone=5723/firelands">Firelands</a>, so this trinket will last you quite a while. The normal version is the second best passive trinket. <br /><br /><a href="/cata/item=65118/crushing-weight">Crushing Weight</a> has a Haste proc, one of our worst secondary stats. <a href="/cata/item=58180/license-to-slay">License to Slay</a> only takes 5-6 seconds to stack, but only provides 380 Strength - not the most helpful for our burst damage. You will also need to reforge the excess hit, and at times it is not possible to reforge all of the excess, hurting the value. Both of these trinkets fall between equal to slightly worse than <a href="/cata/item=56393/heart-of-solace">Heart of Solace</a>.<br /><i><br /><a href="/cata/item=59461/fury-of-angerforge">Fury of Angerforge</a> is not listed here because it is wildly expensive, and takes forever to stack due to a 5-second internal cooldown making it perform extremely poorly. You should absolutely NOT spend money on it. </i><br /><br /><table><br /><tr> <br /><td><b>Rank</b></td><br /><td><b>Item</b></td><br /><td><b>Sockets</b></td><br /><td><b>Source</b></td><br /><td><b>Location</b></td><br /></tr> <br /><br /><tr><td>Best: Active</td><br /><td><a href="/cata/item=68712/impatience-of-youth">Impatience of Youth</a></td><br /><td><br />Exalted with <a href="/cata/faction=1178/hellscreams-reach">Hellscream's Reach</a> or <a href="/cata/faction=1177/baradins-wardens">Baradin's Wardens</a></td><br /><td><a href="/cata/zone=5095/tol-barad">Tol Barad</a></td></tr><br /><br /><tr><td>Best: Passive</td><br /><td><a href="/cata/item=65072/heart-of-rage">Heart of Rage</a></td><br /><td><br />Drops from <a href="/cata/npc=43296/chimaeron">Chimaeron</a></td><br /><td><a href="/cata/zone=5094/blackwing-descent">Blackwing Descent</a></td></tr><br /><br /><tr><td>Optional</td><br /><td><a href="/cata/item=59224/heart-of-rage">Heart of Rage</a></td><br /><td><br />Drops from <a href="/cata/npc=43296/chimaeron">Chimaeron</a></td><br /><td><a href="/cata/zone=5094/blackwing-descent">Blackwing Descent</a></td></tr><br /><br /><tr><td>Optional</td><br /><td><a href="/cata/item=56393/heart-of-solace">Heart of Solace</a></td><br /><td><br />Drops from <a href="/cata/npc=49045/augh">Augh</a> and <a href="/cata/npc=43614/lockmaw">Lockmaw</a></td><br /><td><a href="/cata/zone=5396/lost-city-of-the-tolvir">Lost City of the Tol'vir</a></td></tr><br /><br /><tr><td>Optional</td><br /><td><a href="/cata/item=58180/license-to-slay">License to Slay</a></td><br /><td><br />1650x <a href="/cata/currency=396/valor-points">Valor Points</a></td><br /><td><a href="/cata/zone=1519/stormwind-city">Stormwind City</a>, <a href="/cata/zone=1637/orgrimmar">Orgrimmar</a></td></tr><br /><br /><tr><td>Optional</td><br /><td><a href="/cata/item=65118/crushing-weight">Crushing Weight</a></td><br /><td><br />Drops from <a href="/cata/npc=43735/elementium-monstrosity">Elementium Monstrosity</a></td><br /><td><a href="/cata/zone=5334/the-bastion-of-twilight">The Bastion of Twilight</a></td></tr><br /><br /></table>
"""
